## Environment

See **`.env.example`**. Never commit secrets. Security rule: **`17-security.mdc`**.

| Required | Optional (production) |
|----------|------------------------|
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_SANITY_*` | `RESEND_API_KEY`, `EMAIL_FROM`, `EMAIL_TO` |
| `SANITY_API_TOKEN` | `REVALIDATE_SECRET` |
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL` | `UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_*`, Turnstile keys |

## Layout

See **`14-file-structure.mdc`**. Summary:

```
app/(site)/ api/ studio/
components/{layout,ui,sections,content,seo}/
lib/{types,cache-tags,contact-schema,rate-limit,tailwind.ts,…}/
sanity/{schemaTypes,lib}/
docs/ deploy/ scripts/
```

- Thin `page.tsx`; route-private UI in `app/**/_components/`
- API routes: Zod + rate limit — **`17-security.mdc`**
- CMS: `revalidate = 300` + webhook tags (`setup-revalidation` skill)
- Fetch via `get*` in `sanity/lib/fetchers.ts`

